## Data Licenses

This model is built on publicly available data from several sources. Users of
this model's outputs should be aware of the following:

**NOAA MRMS / MYRORSS data** — Public domain (U.S. Government works). Citation
requested: Lakshmanan et al. (2007), Cintineo et al. (2012), Smith et al.
(2016).

**NCAR Research Data Archive (GridRad / GridRad-Severe)** — Subject to NCAR RDA
terms of service. Non-commercial research use is generally permitted; commercial
use requires a separate agreement. See https://rda.ucar.edu/datasets/ds841.6/

**ERA5 reanalysis (Copernicus Climate Data Store)** — Licensed under the
Copernicus licence. Free for any purpose (including commercial) with attribution.
See https://cds.climate.copernicus.eu/disclaimer-privacy

**NOAA Storm Prediction Center (SPC) severe weather reports** — Public domain
(U.S. Government works). Used for validation only; not a model input. See
https://www.spc.noaa.gov/climo/reports/

The MIT licence above covers only the code and documentation in this
repository. Data files and model outputs derived from third-party sources may
carry additional restrictions; users are responsible for ensuring compliance
with the relevant data licences.
